# @ancplua/* npm packages publish to GitHub Packages (npm.pkg.github.com), not npmjs.
# This scope->registry mapping lets npm install AND Renovate resolve @ancplua/* deps
# (e.g. @ancplua/typespec-otel-semconv). CI auth comes from setup-node
# (NODE_AUTH_TOKEN=GITHUB_TOKEN); local dev needs a GitHub PAT (read:packages) in ~/.npmrc.
@ancplua:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
